+
+### Decisions
+- **Decision Title** — Description [status: pending/approved/rejected]
+
+### Approvals
+- ✓ **Approved Item** by [author] at [timestamp]
+
+### Rejections
+- ✗ **Rejected Item** by [author]: [reason]
